{{!
    This file is part of Moodle - http://moodle.org/

    @template    block_feedback_tracker/sparkline

    Compact 30-day median effective-hours sparkline on a speed axis: fewer
    hours (faster turnaround) render HIGHER. With an optional "desired-speed
    zone" (light-green band anchored at the top 0 → goal, solid baseline at
    0 hours / top edge, dotted line at the goal / minimum-desired-speed
    boundary). Keep in lockstep with the JS port
    amd/src/components/Sparkline.js and classes/output/sparkline.php.

    Context variables required:
    * empty       Truthy when no data points are available
    * width       SVG width in user units
    * height      SVG height in user units
    * polyline    Space-separated "x,y" coordinates for the line
    * haszone     Truthy when the desired-speed zone should be drawn
    * zoney       Y-coordinate of the goal (minimum-desired-speed) line
    * zoneheight  Height of the top-anchored zone band (equals zoney)
    * showlabel   Truthy when there is room for the text caption
    * zonelabel   Localised "Desired speed: 0 to N" caption

    Example context (json):
    {
        "empty": false,
        "width": 120,
        "height": 30,
        "polyline": "0,10 20,15 40,20 60,18 80,22 100,25 120,23",
        "haszone": true,
        "zoney": 12,
        "zoneheight": 12,
        "showlabel": true,
        "zonelabel": "Desired speed: 0 to 24"
    }
}}
<svg class="bft-sparkline" viewBox="0 0 {{width}} {{height}}"
     width="{{width}}" height="{{height}}"
     role="img" aria-label="30-day trend">
    {{#haszone}}
        <rect class="bft-sparkline-zone" x="0" y="0" width="{{width}}" height="{{zoneheight}}"/>
        <line class="bft-sparkline-zone-base" x1="0" y1="0" x2="{{width}}" y2="0"/>
        <line class="bft-sparkline-zone-top" x1="0" y1="{{zoney}}" x2="{{width}}" y2="{{zoney}}"/>
    {{/haszone}}
    {{#empty}}
        <line x1="0" y1="{{height}}" x2="{{width}}" y2="{{height}}" stroke="#cbd5e1" stroke-width="0.5"/>
    {{/empty}}
    {{^empty}}
        <polyline class="bft-sparkline-line" fill="none" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" points="{{polyline}}"/>
    {{/empty}}
    {{#showlabel}}
        <text class="bft-sparkline-zone-label" x="2" y="9">{{zonelabel}}</text>
    {{/showlabel}}
</svg>
